Print a JSON Schema

Usage: sleet schema [KIND]

Arguments:
  [KIND]
          Which schema to print

          Possible values:
          - config:    The fleet spec TOML format (schema/config.schema.json)
          - cli:       Subcommand `--format json` responses, one `$defs` entry per command (schema/cli.schema.json)
          - heartbeat: The heartbeat object body (schema/heartbeat.schema.json)
          
          [default: config]

Options:
  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
